one_reviews_text: bad graphics, not muck stuff, stupid enimes and more.

-Beautiful game in a charming retro style.
-Freely explore a small but exciting open-world island.
-Gameplay is fun, and with the extensive arena combat, there are plenty of opportunities to practice your battlemage skills!
-Plenty of comfort and gameplay options to customize in-game.
There is also a Garage Collective discord channel for connecting with the devs.
